\series default
 is introduced.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In reality peope do buy insurance, and the reason is that they maximize
 utility and not value (even although the expected value is negative).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The premium is always greater than the expected loss (otherwise insurance
